<batch_everything>
⚠️ BATCH-FIRST DEFAULT ⚠️

PARALLEL IS DEFAULT - SEQUENTIAL IS EXCEPTION

Instead of:
1. Read file A
2. Then read file B  
3. Then read file C

ALWAYS:
